            <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem; color: var(--text-secondary);">This proprietary screen filters the entire US equity market to identify small-cap value opportunities using strict fundamental criteria:</p>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Market Capitalization:</strong> Strictly between $300 Million and $2 Billion.</li>
